en_603944_0	Colonel P.K.W.W.M.J.S.B.W Pallekumbura of Gajaba Regiment assumed duties as the 10th Brigade Commander in the 231 Brigade on Monday (2) at the Brigade Headquarters in Kallady.
en_603944_1	To mark the memorable event, the new Brigade Commander planted a sapling in the Brigade Headquarters premises and signed a formal document to signify the acceptance of the new office.
en_603944_2	An All Rank tea table culminated the simple ceremony.
en_603944_3	Staff Officers of the Brigade Headquarters and Other Ranks attended the occasion.
